page_0: "The formula for the blasting powder is quite tricky to balance, and one mistake would be disastrous. Nonetheless, I persevere, for my captain wishes to speed up construction. They've taken the last batch into the mines. I just hope they know what they're doing and don't bring the whole mountain crashing down. I've hidden the remaining fire arrows, for they would be a great temptation for some of these buffoons."
